<H1>Changing the size of the command history</H1>

<P>By default the previous 128 commands are saved in the
command history list. <A HREF="../environment/env3c.html">Set the environment variable</A>
<SAMP>HISTSIZE</SAMP> to save a smaller or larger number of commands. For example:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>HISTSIZE=50;export HISTSIZE</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This will keep a history of the fifty (50) most recent
commands that you have used.</P>

